snippet: Oxford beat Cambridge, 33-15, to clinch a fourth successive Varsity Match, but its win was overshadowed by the first red card in the 141-year history of the game.
abstract: Oxford beats Cambridge, 33-15, to clinch a fourth successive Varsity Match in rugby, but win is overshadowed by the first red card in the 141-year history of the game.

headline.main: Red Card Issued in Oxford Win
